Table 'devices'
	Contains the list of wireless network devices that will be used
	- name(varchar): name of network interface to use

Table 'authorized'
	The list of all authorized Wi-Fi APs. Action will be taken agains every AP detected not found in the table.
	- name(varchar): Access Point SSID
	- mac(varchar): Physical address of the Access Point in the format "aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff"